txt.en: You have defeated many prowling battle-cats.
The vicious battle-cats of the Jangovar have begun to stray from their masters in Utterby, threatening the peoples and wild beasts of the Ironfold.
You have defeated many of the prowling battle-cats of the Jangovar. While more still remain in Utterby, you have done well to protect the peoples and beasts of the Ironfold.
Prowling battle-cats can be found roaming outside Utterby in the Ironfold.\n\nYou have encountered a number of prowling battle-cats and should defeat them.

While exploring the foothills of the Ironfold, you have encountered a great number of the battle-cats used in battle by the Jangovar. With Utterby seized by the Jangovar, the battle-cats now prowl the Ironfold and threaten its inhabitants. You should defeat the battle-cats of the Jangovar before they can bring greater harm to the peoples and beasts of the Ironfold.
